cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CV 

This paper is about evaluating sentence representations in Polish, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses various machine learning techniques and models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of different models, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper mentions the use of embeddings in image captioning, which could relate to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
